# ===== CONFIGURATION VALIDATION =====
#
# The following environment variables are required for full functionality:
# - PARLANT_ENABLED
# - PARLANT_API_BASE_URL (if using external Parlant service)
# - PARLANT_API_KEY (if using external Parlant service)
#
# Optional but recommended for production:
# - PARLANT_LOG_LEVEL
# - PARLANT_AUDIT_RETENTION_DAYS
# - PARLANT_DATA_CLASSIFICATION
# - PARLANT_ENABLE_GDPR_COMPLIANCE (if handling EU data)
